                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Lee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Day</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Havana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-01-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 25, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>At an interview authorities profess to think United States has ulterior purpose
                    in sending ship. Say it will obstruct autonomy, produce excitement, and most
                    probably a demonstration. Ask that it is not done until they can get
                    instructions from Madrid, and say that if for friendly motives, as claimed,
                    delay unimportant.</p>
            </div>
